93
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:31,0000
We were all the time, maybe naively, believing that you...

94
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:37,0000
Now, not you personally, but the whole gang of Syriza, that you had a B plan.

95
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:39,0000
Something secretly to...

96
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:44,0000
Sorry for the vulgarity to squeeze the testicles of European Union.

97
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:51,0000
