271
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:22,0000
So I was saying to him, "I'm not signing."

272
00:22:22,000 --> 00:22:29,0000
Imagine you owe money to the bank. You can't repay because your income has come down.

273
00:22:29,000 --> 00:22:36,0000
