00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:29,0000
I take my phone out and I call Tsipras in front of him, put it on speakerphone.

294
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:36,0000
I said, "Wolfgang just said to me that he proposed that we get out of the euro and that a large part of the debt is written off, of course.

295
00:24:36,000 --> 00:24:47,0000
If you don't have euros, you don't pay in euros. You pay in souvlaki or pistachios or something."

296
00:24:47,000 --> 00:24:52,0000
"I've got a question for you, Alexei. Do you authorize me to have this discussion with him?"

297
00:24:52,000 --> 00:25:00,0000
