298
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:04,0000
In front of him. Put the phone down. Your turn.

299
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:09,0000
He said, "I'm not going to speak to her now, I'm going to speak to her tomorrow, I'll call you back."

300
00:25:09,000 --> 00:25:13,0000
We talked again a couple of days later. So what happened?

301
00:25:13,000 --> 00:25:18,0000
He said, "Look, I fear that if I tell her she's not going to give the okay."

302
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:24,0000
So I was playing that game and in the end he never got the okay to discuss this with me.

303
00:25:24,000 --> 00:25:37,0000
But you see, so Grexit was never their strategy. It was Schäuble's strategy and Merkel always vetoed it.

304
00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:47,0000
In the end, to cut a long story short, I think that on the balance of probabilities,

305
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:52,0000
