00:43:57,000 --> 00:44:01,0000
and then they go home, and that's time for themselves.

568
00:44:01,000 --> 00:44:06,0000
Today you have a proletariat, a working class, which is shrinking, shrinking, shrinking,

569
00:44:06,000 --> 00:44:13,0000
and increasingly everybody is producing capital directly for these fiefdoms.

570
00:44:13,000 --> 00:44:18,0000
Every time you have your phone and you walk around, Google knows where you are,

571
00:44:18,000 --> 00:44:22,0000
and that enriches the software of Google Maps.

